spec_data.Name: cvs2cl
spec_data.Description:
cvs2cl generates GNU-style ChangeLogs for a CVS working copy using the
output of the "cvs log" command.  The script originally came from the
open source CVS book at http://cvsbook.red-bean.com/.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:18:02 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate ChangeLogs from CVS working copies
